Evicted Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Brighto has said he would kiss Nengi if given the opportunity. Brighto said this during his media tour with one of the sponsors of the show, Betway on Thursday. When asked who he would kiss among Nengi, Wathoni and Dorathy, Brighto chose Nengi. “I’ll kiss Nengi if asked to choose among those three female housemates,” Brighto said. He further revealed that he has plans for Wathoni outside the house. Brighto, Wathoni and Tolanibaj were evicted on Sunday after they scored the lowest votes from viewers. Brighto nicknames as ‘Lord Baelish’ was close to Wathoni and Dorathy while in the house.